    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for a reliable ride that's ready for its next adventure? This vehicle is in good, solid condition and has been well-maintained to ensure it's dependable for your daily needs. With a clean interior and a smooth drive, it's a fantastic choice for anyone who values quality and performance without the showroom price tag. Come take it for a spin and see why this well-cared-for car is the perfect fit for you!",
