      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 46
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional, showroom-quality vehicle that satisfies even the most discerning collector. This car has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled garage and has never seen inclement weather. The exterior finish is flawless, featuring a deep, mirror-like luster with absolutely no rock chips, swirl marks, or door dings, further protected by a multi-layer ceramic coating. Inside, the cabin remains in 'time-capsule' condition; the premium leather bolsters show no creasing, the carpets are pristine under original protector mats, and the interior still retains that distinct new-car scent. Every electronic feature, from the infotainment system to the seat heaters, operates with factory precision. Under the hood, the engine bay is spotless. The vehicle boasts a comprehensive service history with all maintenance performed exclusively by certified technicians using OEM parts. With remarkably low mileage and a documented history of adult ownership, this is a rare opportunity to own a turn-key masterpiece that looks and drives exactly as it did on the showroom floor.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
